# Jobs Data Directory

Store raw job listings here.

Structure:
```
data/jobs/
├── 2025-01/
│   ├── 2025-01-15.json      # Daily batch
│   ├── 2025-01-16.json
│   └── ...
├── 2025-02/
│   └── ...
└── archive/                  # > 90 days old
    └── ...
```

Each JSON file contains an array of Job objects validated against `../schema/job.json`.
